66
00:03:37.604 --> 00:03:42.316
From moving from software engineer all the
way to manager, if you're lucky, right?

67
00:03:42.316 --> 00:03:46.211
A lot of companies don't have that,
but some do.

68
00:03:46.211 --> 00:03:49.688
And then sometimes you have a role
transition over time, where it's agreed by

69
00:03:49.688 --> 00:03:52.809
your manager, it's a small enough team,
the blast radius is small.

70
00:03:52.809 --> 00:03:56.417
